        <deprecated>false</deprecated>
        <description>Retrieves Recipients using the specified class. Class must implement the interface PatientConnect.PC_ReminderQueue.RecipientFinder. Use this when a recipient cannot be obtained directly using Recipient Field API Name or more than one recipient needs to be retrieved.</description>
